measure.CatchLine: Allows a landlord to terminate residential tenancy upon third material violation or late payment upon 30 days' notice with no right to cure.
measure.MeasureSummary:
Digest: This Act allows a landlord to evict upon a tenant's third breach. (Flesch Readability Score: 74.8). 
	Allows a landlord to terminate residential tenancy upon third material violation or late payment upon 30 days' notice with no right to cure.
measure.RelatingTo: Relating to termination of residential tenancy for repeated violations.
measure.FiscalImpact: May have fiscal impact, but no statement yet issued
measure.RevenueImpact: May have revenue impact, but no statement yet issued
